OL,6,FA family who complained they could
OL,7,Fhear hospital staff laughing as their
OL,8,Fson's life support machine was
OL,9,Fswitched off were given "poor" care,
OL,10,Fan investigation has found.
OL,12,FFive-year-old Muhammad Ayaan Haroon,
OL,13,Fknown as Ayaan, died at Sheffield
OL,14,FChildren's Hospital in March 2023,
OL,15,Feight days after he was admitted with
OL,16,Fbreathing problems.
OL,18,FAyaan's father Haroon Rashid, 42,
OL,19,Fcomplained about a "catalogue of
OL,20,Fcatastrophic errors" in his son's care
OL,21,Fthat he believes cost Ayaan his life.
