OL,4,Claughing as son died given 'poor' care
OL,6,FMr Rashid, a taxi driver, has now
OL,7,Fcalled for a second investigation,
OL,8,Fsaying his family "can't trust" the
OL,9,Ffindings.
OL,11,FHe told the PA news agency: "Although
OL,12,Fit's very critical of the care my son
OL,13,Freceived, the main thing for us as a
OL,14,Ffamily is despite it saying his care
OL,15,Fwas mismanaged, it still says the
OL,16,Foutcome would not have changed. We as
OL,17,Fa family can't accept that.
OL,19,F"The way I see it there was a
OL,20,Fcatalogue of catastrophic errors that
OL,21,Fwere made... that cost him his life.
OL,26,@pD@SOUpD@_O]sD@]OU{D@AOU
