OL,4,Claughing as son died given 'poor' care
OL,6,F"We want a second investigation, for
OL,7,Fthe truth and for the report to
OL,8,Freflect the true care that my son
OL,9,Freceived. Our ultimate goal is for
OL,10,Fgenuine lessons to be learned."
OL,12,FThe report said during his life Ayaan,
OL,13,Fwho had a history of respiratory
OL,14,Fproblems and a rare genetic condition
OL,15,Fcalled Hace 1, was admitted to
OL,16,FSheffield Children's Hospital on five
OL,17,Foccasions with respiratory illnesses.
OL,18,FOn each occasion there was an
OL,19,Fescalation of his symptoms and the
OL,20,Ftreatment he needed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@_O]
