OL,6,FOn 5 March 2023, he became unwell at
OL,7,Fhome and was admitted with a lower
OL,8,Frespiratory tract infection. When his
OL,9,Fcondition deteriorated he was
OL,10,Ftransferred to the paediatric
OL,11,Fintensive care unit (PICU), where he
OL,12,Fdied on 13 March.
OL,14,FOut of 736 complaint points submitted
OL,15,Fby Ayaan's family, investigators
OL,16,Fupheld 307 points (42%), partly upheld
OL,17,F171 (23%), did not uphold 174 (24%)
OL,18,Fand could not substantiate 61 (8%)
OL,19,Fpoints. They said 23 points (3%) did
OL,20,Fnot require an outcome judgement.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/14
