OL,4,Claughing as son died given 'poor' care
OL,6,FThe draft report sent to Ayaan's
OL,7,Ffamily found that bereavement care
OL,8,Fprovided to them was "poor" and the
OL,9,Fcultural sensitivity shown after his
OL,10,Fdeath was "substantially inadequate".
OL,12,FInvestigators found this "undoubtedly
OL,13,Fadded to the trauma of the family".
OL,15,FThe draft report said Ayaan became
OL,16,Fmore unwell each time he was admitted
OL,17,Fto hospital and Hace 1 may have
OL,18,Faffected his ability to fight viral
OL,19,Finfections himself.
