OL,6,FInvestigators said there were aspects
OL,7,Fof Ayaan's care that did not meet
OL,8,Fexpected standards, including the fact
OL,9,Fthat he should have been started on
OL,10,Fhigh flow oxygen therapy sooner and a
OL,11,Ffour-hour delay in admitting him to
OL,12,FPICU because of bed and staff capacity
OL,13,Fissues.
OL,15,FThe report said the medical clinical
OL,16,Fhandover on the inpatient ward Ayaan
OL,17,Fwas initially admitted to "was chaotic
OL,18,Fand ineffective" and "had the
OL,19,Fpotential for the sickest children not
OL,20,Fto be adequately handed over at the
OL,21,Fchange of shift".
OL,26,@yD@[OUzD@PO]zD@VOU}D@PO]
