OL,4,Claughing as son died given 'poor' care
OL,6,FThe report found there was "poor
OL,7,Fcommunication" around the likelihood
OL,8,Fof Ayaan's survival and a failure to
OL,9,Fprovide timely bereavement support
OL,10,Fafter his death.
OL,12,FThe family have previously complained
OL,13,Fthey could hear staff laughing in a
OL,14,Fnearby room during Ayaan's final
OL,15,Fmoments, and the report said that as
OL,16,Fthe unit was busy there was no side
OL,17,Froom available "to support a private
OL,18,Fdignified death which, while
OL,19,Funavoidable, added to the family's
OL,20,Fdistress".
OL,26,@nD@\OUoD@NO]yD@POU|D@IO]
