OL,6,FThe investigation found "no evidence
OL,7,Fof systemic or individual harassment
OL,8,For victimisation" but said staff did
OL,9,Fnot find out if there were specific
OL,10,Fcultural wishes of the family when
OL,11,Fperforming Ayaan's last rites and in
OL,12,Fthe management of Ayaan's body.
OL,14,FThey said the fact that this was not
OL,15,Fcovered in the NHS trust's policy "may
OL,16,Fbe seen as indirectly discriminatory".
