OL,6,FThe report made 15 recommendations,
OL,7,Fincluding; alternative strategies for
OL,8,Fventilatory support on the ward where
OL,9,Fan intensive care bed is not
OL,10,Favailable; guidelines on handling the
OL,11,F"immediate post-death period";
OL,12,Fconsidering whether a member of staff
OL,13,Fwho shares the same ethnic background
OL,14,Fshould act as a link worker for the
OL,15,Fbereavement process; and organising
OL,16,Funconscious bias training for all
OL,17,Fclinical staff.
