OL,6,FDr Jeff Perring, executive medical
OL,7,Fdirector at Sheffield Children's NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust, said: "We express
OL,9,Four deepest condolences to Ayaan's
OL,10,Ffamily for their loss.
OL,12,F"We commissioned an independent
OL,13,Finvestigation into the care and
OL,14,Ftreatment of Ayaan. The draft report,
OL,15,Fwith recommendations, has now been
OL,16,Fshared with Ayaan's family for their
OL,17,Ffeedback.
